title: Gotham Girls all 3 seasons .swf (vid not comics)
description:
Got kids?

Just want some stupid fun yourself?

Here is all 3 seasons of the flash videos "Gotham Girls" from WB.
30 videos/games in all.
When vid starts you have the option of playing the (crappy but OK for young kids) puzzle game that is interactive with the video, or just watching the (rather short) cartoon.

I believe this is also available on the BoP DVD set, but I have no clue if that's game/video or just video.

This is meant to be played on a computer.
You'll need flashplayer, but everyone on the planet has that right?
